：中国澳门</strong><br /><strong>03：中国澳门<br />08：阿拉伯联合酋长国迪拜，议程（重新安排）<br /></strong></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> 2023 D&amp;E WORLD TOUR FANCON – 【欢乐派对】 </p><p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4cd.png" alt="📍" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> 11/12 温哥华<br /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4cd.png" alt="📍" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> 11/28 多伦多</p><p>我们很高兴宣布“+及更多”国家/地区。<br />加拿大见<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f917.png" alt="🤗" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f917.png" alt="🤗" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><br />请继续关注更多详情！ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%EC%8A%88%ED%8D%BC%EC%A3%BC%EB%8B%88%EC%96%B4DnE?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#슈퍼주니어DnE</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/SUPERJUNIORDnE?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#SUPERJUNIORDnE</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%EC%8A%88%ED%8D%BC%EC%A3%BC%EB%8B%88%EC%96%B4?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#슈퍼주니어</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/SUPERJUNIOR?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#SUPERJUNIOR</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%EC%9D%80%ED%98%81?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#은혁</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/EUNHYUK?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#EUNHYUK</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%EB%8F%99%ED%95%B4?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#동해</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DONGHAE?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#DONGHAE</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DElight?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#DElight</a> <a href="https://t.co/meS5Hp2ncx">pic.twitter.com/meS5Hp2ncx</a></p><p> — SUPERJUNIOR D&amp;E 官员 (@SJ_DnE_official) <a href="https://twitter.com/SJ_DnE_official/status/1705945650276552738?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 24 日<